# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format follows [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/) and adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

---

## [3.0.0] - 2025-12-01  
_The Modernization Release_

### Added
- Full compatibility with WordPress 6.8+ and PHP 8.3
- New Template Category Filter UI on `wp-signup.php`
- AJAX-driven template list refresh during site signup
- Modernized admin UI under **Network Admin â†’ Templates**
- README.md and changelog documentation

### Changed
- Refactored deprecated multisite admin menu functions
- Updated template data models and sanitization
- Improved UX for template selection screens
- Enhanced database querying for category filters

### Fixed
- Broken Network Admin menu links for Templates
- Template categories not saving or displaying correctly
- Template selection toolbar failing to load on signup
- JS errors preventing category filtering behavior
- Various warnings/notices thrown under PHP 8+

---

## [2.9.0] - 2025-11-10  
_Legacy compatibility and initial refactoring_

### Added
- Compatibility fixes for WordPress 6.x
- Initial conversion of legacy code to modern standards

### Removed
- Dead code and abandoned admin pages

---

